              <h1 class="post-title">SimplyBook</h1>
            </header>

            <div class="post-content">
              

<p>Transform your barbershop with smart booking management. Streamline appointments, manage staff schedules, and delight customers with our powerful Shopify-integrated barbershop booking system.</p>

<p>Built for modern barbershops who want to focus on what matters most - providing excellent service to their customers while running an efficient business.</p>

<h2>Key Features</h2>

<p><strong>Smart Scheduling</strong> - Automated appointment booking with real-time availability. Customers can book 24/7 with instant confirmations.</p>

<p><strong>Staff Management</strong> - Manage your team's schedules, track performance, and handle availability with ease. Perfect for multi-staff operations.</p>

<p><strong>Shopify Integration</strong> - Seamlessly integrated with your Shopify store. Sync products, manage inventory, and process payments all in one place.</p>

<p><strong>Mobile Ready</strong> - Fully responsive design works perfectly on all devices. Manage your barbershop from anywhere, anytime.</p>

<p><strong>Analytics & Reports</strong> - Track your business performance with detailed analytics. Understand your customers and optimize your operations.</p>

<p><strong>Smart Notifications</strong> - Automated reminders for customers and staff. Reduce no-shows and keep everyone informed.</p>

<h2>Why Choose Our Barbershop Booking System?</h2>

<p><strong>Save Time</strong> - Reduce administrative work by up to 70% with automated booking and scheduling.</p>

<p><strong>Increase Revenue</strong> - Reduce no-shows by 40% and capture more bookings with 24/7 online availability.</p>

<p><strong>Happy Customers</strong> - Provide a seamless booking experience that your customers will love and recommend.</p>

<p><strong>Secure & Reliable</strong> - Enterprise-grade security with 99.9% uptime guarantee. Your data is always safe.</p>

<h2>Getting Started</h2>

<p>Welcome to your barbershop booking system! Follow these steps to get your business up and running:</p>

<ol>
<li><strong>Access Your Dashboard:</strong> Navigate to your Shopify admin panel and find the Barbershop Pro app</li>
<li><strong>Complete Initial Configuration:</strong> Set up your shop information, locations, and basic settings</li>
<li><strong>Add Your Staff:</strong> Create staff profiles with photos, contact information, and specialties</li>
<li><strong>Configure Services:</strong> Set up your service offerings with pricing and duration</li>
<li><strong>Set Availability:</strong> Define when your staff are available for appointments</li>
</ol>

<h2>Staff Management</h2>

<p>From the staff list, you can:</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>View Details:</strong> Click on any staff member's name to access their profile</li>
<li><strong>Edit Information:</strong> Update contact details, bio, or photo</li>
<li><strong>Set Availability:</strong> Configure when each staff member is available</li>
<li><strong>Manage Services:</strong> Assign which services each staff member can perform</li>
<li><strong>Deactivate Staff:</strong> Temporarily disable staff without deleting their data</li>
</ul>

<h2>Booking System</h2>

<p>Your customers can book appointments through your integrated booking widget:</p>

<ol>
<li><strong>Select Service:</strong> Choose from your available services (haircut, beard trim, etc.)</li>
<li><strong>Pick Date & Time:</strong> View real-time availability and select preferred slot</li>
<li><strong>Choose Staff:</strong> Select their preferred barber (optional)</li>
<li><strong>Enter Details:</strong> Provide contact information and any special requests</li>
<li><strong>Confirm Booking:</strong> Review and confirm their appointment</li>
</ol>

<h2>Shopify Integration</h2>

<p>Your barbershop services are automatically synced with your Shopify store:</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Service Products:</strong> Each booking service becomes a Shopify product</li>
<li><strong>Inventory Management:</strong> Track service availability and capacity</li>
<li><strong>Pricing Sync:</strong> Service prices automatically update in Shopify</li>
<li><strong>Product Variants:</strong> Different service options (e.g., haircut vs. haircut + beard)</li>
</ul>

<h2>Pricing</h2>

<p><strong>Starter - $29/month</strong> - Perfect for small barbershops. Up to 2 staff members, 100 bookings per month, basic scheduling, email support.</p>

<p><strong>Professional - $59/month</strong> - Ideal for growing barbershops. Up to 5 staff members, unlimited bookings, advanced scheduling, Shopify integration, analytics & reports, priority support.</p>

<p><strong>Enterprise - $99/month</strong> - For large barbershop chains. Unlimited staff members, multi-location support, custom integrations, advanced analytics, API access, dedicated support.</p>

<h2>Getting Help</h2>

<p>If you need additional support:</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Check the FAQ:</strong> Common questions and answers</li>
<li><strong>Contact Support:</strong> Reach out to our support team</li>
<li><strong>Video Tutorials:</strong> Watch step-by-step guides</li>
<li><strong>Community Forum:</strong> Connect with other barbershop owners</li>
</ul>

